pics.caption: Ive always encouraged my children to look for beauty in everything even if at first it appears theres nothing beautiful abt what obviously is not pretty at first glance.... so we were driving along tonite and my sweet little Selena says "mami stop" at the top of her lungs & she tells me "I see a beautiful giraffe!" I'm thinking to myself "what the heck", lol! This shot was captured at a dilapidated putput golf course falling in disarray. And this was Selena's one beautiful thing she found :)) Way to go baby girl!!
